      "1 <= number of nodes <= 10^4",
      "0 <= Node.val <= 10^4"
    ],
    "inputFormat": "The input is the root of a binary tree where each node has a unique value.",
    "outputFormat": "The output is the root of the resulting doubly linked list.",
